Assay Name: Drug concentration required to achieve 50% kill of EMT6 cells under hypoxic conditions.
Drug concentration required to achieve 50% kill of EMT6 cells under oxygenated conditions.

Inhibition of recombinant His6-tagged Pseudomonas aeruginosa PqsD expressed in Escherichia coli BL21 (deltaDE3) using anthraniloyl-CoA/beta-ketodecanoic acid as substrate assessed as HHQ formation preincubated for 10 mins followed by substrate addition by HPLC/MS-MS analysis
